Packages 
Package Description
Catalano.Core
The Catalano.Core contains common classes used by other namespaces of the framework and classes, which can be used independently for various purposes.
Catalano.Fuzzy
The Catalano.Fuzzy namespace contains set of interfaces and classes to operate with fuzzy sets.
Catalano.Imaging
The Catalano.Image contains base class for manipulation of pixels.
Catalano.Imaging.Filters
The Catalano.Imaging.Filters namespace contains collection classes, which provide different image processing filters.
Catalano.Imaging.Tools
The Catalano.Imaging.Tools namespace contains collection classes, which provide different image moments, analysis textures.
Catalano.MachineLearning
The Catalano.MachineLearning namespace contains interfaces and classes for different algorithms of machine learning.
Catalano.Math
The Catalano.Math namespace contains set of math utilities, which are used by other Catalano framework's namespaces or may be used individually.
Catalano.Math.Geometry
The Catalano.Math.Geometry namespace contains set of geometry utilities, which are used by other Catalano namespaces or may be used individually.
Catalano.Math.Transforms
The Catalano.Math.Transforms namespace contains set of transforms.
Catalano.Math.Wavelets
The Catalano.Math.Wavelets namespace contains Wavelets transform such as the Haar Wavelet transforms.
Catalano.Neuro
The Catalano.Neuro namespace contains interfaces and classes for neural networks computations.
Catalano.Neuro.Learning
The Catalano.Neuro.Learning namespace contains interfaces and classes for neurons and neural networks learning.
Catalano.Statistics
The Catalano.Statistics namespace contains set of statistics utilities, which are used by other Catalano framework's namespaces or may be used individually.
Catalano.Statistics.Distributions
The Catalano.Statistics.Distribution namespace contains statistical distributions.
